sequenceDiagram
    actor User as Super Admin, Admin, or Guard
    participant UI as JavaFX Password Recovery Screens
    participant API as Spring Boot Auth API
    participant Service as PasswordResetService
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Audit as AuditLogDAO

    User->>UI: Start forgot-password flow
    UI->>API: POST /auth/password-reset/request
    API->>Service: create reset route or token
    Service->>DB: Resolve account and persist reset state
    API-->>UI: Reset instructions
    User->>UI: Submit token and new password
    UI->>API: POST /auth/password-reset/confirm
    API->>Service: validate token and password
    Service->>DB: Update password_hash
    Service->>Audit: Write USER_UPDATED
    API-->>UI: Password reset result
